(Written by Xiang Bei, author
of Heard You Got a Dog Outside? Divorce!)

13
00:00:59,020 --> 00:00:59,819
Hello everyone.

14
00:00:59,820 --> 00:01:02,270
I am Chen Zhiqing,
the male supporting lead in this project.

15
00:01:02,980 --> 00:01:04,390
Did I read it wrong?

16
00:01:04,390 --> 00:01:07,139
Is superstar Chen Zhiqing playing
a mere supporting role in our project?

17
00:01:07,140 --> 00:01:07,419
Yes.

18
00:01:07,420 --> 00:01:08,470
I can't figure it out.

19
00:01:08,700 --> 00:01:11,179
Is he being blackmailed?

20
00:01:11,180 --> 00:01:12,470
I don't know.

21
00:01:15,220 --> 00:01:17,150
Why did you join this show?

22
00:01:19,100 --> 00:01:21,510
This drama is a big S+ project.

23
00:01:21,540 --> 00:01:22,419
But you have mostly

24
00:01:22,420 --> 00:01:24,470
joined big productions from S+.

25
00:01:26,820 --> 00:01:29,030
I like this character
in this drama very much.

26
00:01:32,940 --> 00:01:34,499
Are you actually blackmailed

27
00:01:34,500 --> 00:01:36,070
by our company?

28
00:01:39,940 --> 00:01:41,219
Now that everyone is here,

29
00:01:41,220 --> 00:01:42,430
let's begin.

30
00:01:56,820 --> 00:01:58,550
When did I become your assistant?

31
