in the utility room.

43
00:03:32,660 --> 00:03:33,739
A photo?

44
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:34,790
I didn't see it.

45
00:03:35,820 --> 00:03:36,859
It's that photo.

46
00:03:36,860 --> 00:03:38,230
