48
00:03:41,500 --> 00:03:42,099
Okay.

49
00:03:42,100 --> 00:03:43,270
You're denying it, are you?

50
00:03:43,820 --> 00:03:44,830
Tell me this,

51
00:03:45,420 --> 00:03:46,830
last night, in the living room,

52
00:03:47,300 --> 00:03:48,550
