to play the leading role.

58
00:04:38,820 --> 00:04:40,139
This is too surprising.

59
00:04:40,140 --> 00:04:41,619
She hasn't appeared yet.

60
00:04:41,620 --> 00:04:43,670
She probably won't attend
the press conference.

61
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:47,880
It's unheard of. A drama without
the leading woman at the press conference.

62
00:04:57,220 --> 00:04:59,390
Here she comes.

63
00:05:00,300 --> 00:05:01,670
So she's the female lead.

64
00:05:02,180 --> 00:05:03,670
Incredible aura.

65
00:05:10,740 --> 00:05:12,019
Sorry, everyone.

66
00:05:12,020 --> 00:05:13,190
I'm late.

67
00:05:25,300 --> 00:05:26,179
Hello everyone.

68
00:05:26,180 --> 00:05:28,990
I am Mu Chenxi,
the female lead of "Misaligned Lover".

69
00:05:53,780 --> 00:05:55,139
No matter what you say,

70
00:05:55,140 --> 00:05:56,299
I can't comprehend it.

71
00:05:56,300 --> 00:05:57,339
For the sake of Mu Chenxi,

72
00:05:57,340 --> 00:05:58,579
you gave up on a leading role

73
00:05:58,580 --> 00:05:59,950
and came here to suffer.

74
00:06:01,540 --> 00:06:02,419
Okay.

75
00:06:02,420 --> 00:06:04,270
I'll shut up and stop talking, okay?

76
00:06:15,900 --> 00:06:16,990
Zhiqing.

77
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:18,550
I bet you are tired.

78
00:06:18,580 --> 00:06:20,150
Here, drink some water.

79
00:06:21,540 --> 00:06:22,550
I'm alright.

80
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:24,430
I have my own.

81
00:06:30,780 --> 00:06:31,859
Zhiqing,

82
00:06:31,860 --> 00:06:32,859
I just

83
00:06:32,860 --> 00:06:35,990
overheard your conversation
with your agent.

84
00:06:38,060 --> 00:06:39,670
I don't mean any harm.

85
00:06:39,860 --> 00:06:41,299
I just think

86
00:06:41,300 --> 00:06:43,939
your many sacrifices for Mu Chenxi

87
00:06:43,940 --> 00:06:45,350
are not worth it at all.

88
00:06:45,540 --> 00:06:46,859
That's my business.

89
00:06:46,860 --> 00:06:48,390
Not yours.

90
00:06:48,540 --> 00:06:50,990
I just think it's unfair for you.

91
00:06:56,260 --> 00:06:57,139
Zhiqing.

92
00:06:57,140 --> 00:06:59,190
This is your upcoming schedule.

93
00:06:59,540 --> 00:07:00,470
Okay.

94
00:07:00,620 --> 00:07:01,779
Here, have a look.

95
00:07:01,780 --> 00:07:03,219
Raise your arm a little higher.

96
00:07:03,220 --> 00:07:04,059
Move back.

97
00:07:04,060 --> 00:07:05,630
Put this foot to the back.

98
00:07:06,860 --> 00:07:07,830
That's right.

99
00:07:11,980 --> 00:07:13,670
Okay, turn around.

100
00:07:15,700 --> 00:07:17,230
Turn around again.

101
00:07:26,980 --> 00:07:28,550
Pay attention to your words and deeds.

102
00:07:42,060 --> 00:07:43,059
Are you okay?

103
00:07:43,060 --> 00:07:43,899
How are you?

104
00:07:43,900 --> 00:07:44,550
I'm alright.

105
00:07:45,460 --> 00:07:46,259
Yan Lidong.

106
00:07:46,260 --> 00:07:47,390
Are you okay?

107
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:13,299
Slow down.

108
00:08:13,300 --> 00:08:14,459
Are you okay?

109
00:08:14,460 --> 00:08:15,670
Does it hurt?

110
00:08:17,580 --> 00:08:19,240
- Not at all.
- How can you still laugh?

111
00:08:20,500 --> 00:08:21,990
You should take a break.

112
00:08:22,620 --> 00:08:23,470
Okay.

113
