126
00:08:46,500 --> 00:08:47,139
Who?

127
00:08:47,140 --> 00:08:47,990
Who is it?

128
00:08:48,780 --> 00:08:49,750
Zhao Qian.

129
00:08:50,340 --> 00:08:51,390
Where did she go?

130
00:08:51,580 --> 00:08:53,350
